---
title: Seared Pork Steak & Extra Baby Broccoli with Creamy Coconut Laksa Sauce & Crushed Peanuts
description: Steamed rice provides the perfect base for pan-seared pork and sautéed greens that'll have you experiencing a magical fusion feast with ease. For the big finish, pull the rabbit out of the hat by topping your pork with a creamy Asian coconut sauce. Tada!
